com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.metamodel

Class Entity<T extends ManagedObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dkharrat.nexusdata.metamodel.Entity<T>

  • public class Entity<T extends ManagedObject>
extends Object
    An Entity represents the ManagedObject's metadata. It is analogous to a Java's class. An instance of an Entity is of supertype ManagedObject. An entity is composed of multiple properties, which are analogous to a class' member fields.
